---
title: "The Second Batch of New Hymns!"
author: "Joey Stanley"
date: "2024-09-18"
date-modified: last-modified
categories: 
  - general
  - frequency
  - new hymns
reference-location: margin
---










On September 12th, 2025, the church released the second batch of new hymns. In [a previous post](/posts/new_hymns_batch1), I covered in detail as much as I could about the first batch of hymns and how they rolled out between June 2 and September 8th. This page covers period between when the second batch came out and when the third batch came out on Febrary 13, 2025. Currently I have data from 8,726 sacrament meetings from 1,409 wards from this range.

But first, here's how much data I have for each week, just so you have an idea of what I'm working with. 



